<h2 class="bold font-l">BCG - Charades</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
To ensure they don't get caught by the librarian, the Greens rely on sign language and pantomiming whenever they need to say something, with their thoughts telling what they are saying. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="e31iw4" data-video-descrip="(At least I'm safe inside my mind...)" data-video-title="SpongeBob SquarePants" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/e31iw4_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/e31iw4.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/InnerMonologueConversation" data-video-tropename="Inner Monologue Conversation" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/SpongeBobSquarePants" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/e31iw4.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">SpongeBob Squar...</span></p>
</a>
</div>
